tid":371182,"uid":48328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T15:08:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>時間唔岩<br />\n平時有朋友去登別都會叫佢順便去白老町食埋牛<br />\n睇Day3打後小樽同札幌行程，其實冇車都得</blockquote><br />\n巴打意思係邊度時間唔岩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n白老町我睇下先 thx anyway<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86abacf3944f6587351d7a2af7644ba4dc75a9c3","tid":371182,"uid":74012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T21:22:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我後日拎車<br />\n第一日諗住主打富良野 美瑛<br />\n第二日早上去小樽, 行一陣 之後要落一落苫小牧</blockquote><br />\n苫小牧我都有諗 不過最衰我自己唔食北寄貝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係因為係果邊既日本朋友要去苫小牧, 我先安排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家0522, 準備食早餐再入機場"},{"pid":"188bb9870cbf6e2414b7db8ad1b20a0d08d74bdd","tid":371182,"uid":74012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T22:29:01.000Z","msg":"我租果架係日產march<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係香港渣慣"},{"pid":"eee7380eb2f9def14a4f0f2fe2987f4432382bfc","tid":371182,"uid":48328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T01:15:27.000Z","msg":"返到公司推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴絲打試過D一泊二食既溫泉酒店可以分享下?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7363d28e173c35e3e50d18f648d668f130ed0f7","tid":371182,"uid":70195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T03:09:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>時間唔岩<br />\n平時有朋友去登別都會叫佢順便去白老町食埋牛<br />\n睇Day3打後小樽同札幌行程，其實冇車都得</blockquote><br />\n巴打意思係邊度時間唔岩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n白老町我睇下先 thx anyway<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我見你第1日