09e18d79a4","tid":371182,"uid":133959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T11:27:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我主要想問下我個路線順唔順其實?<br />\n新千歲&rarr;登別&rarr;洞爺湖&rarr;余市&rarr;小樽&rarr;札幌&rarr;新千歲<br />\n地圖上睇就順既, 但要行國道, 如果唔行國道, 其實係咪兜好多路?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n順就一定順啦，好標准既行法。<br />\n行咩路到時你根據時間研究下GPS最好，無料優先個時間岩既咪行國道，趕時間咪用有料優先上高速囉，因為自動車道你可以超速，好多時你會快過標個時間好多到達。<br />\nday2蒸餾所5點收工，guide tour最後一場係3點半，你研究下你去唔去得切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ee55888b78032f26bc7d28666968f379e42225a","tid":371182,"uid":74012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T00:20:50.000Z","msg":"已上車<br />\n豐田 vitz"},{"pid":"739832d86d8b2620bdcc7756ab39a8c1b1fe66ef","tid":371182,"uid":74012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T06:15:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/p1w89m6c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fp1w89m6c&h=c17cb619&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fdba0943147b58f60f2e20e8cc443f17fdcd07fc","tid":371182,"uid":48328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:23:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/p1w89m6c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fp1w89m6c&h=c17cb619&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n架車行左幾多里？"},{"pid":"8553a0d88d4a0bcfa712adc5cf0661393e362910","tid":371182,"uid":48328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:24:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我主要想問下我個路線順唔順其實?<br />\n新千歲&rarr;登別&rarr;洞爺湖&rarr;余市&rarr;小樽&rarr;札幌&rarr;新千歲<br />\n地圖上睇就順既, 但要行國道, 如果唔行國道, 其實係咪兜好多路?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n順就一定順啦，好標准既行法。<br />\n行咩路到時你根據時間研究下GPS最好，無料優先個時間岩既咪行國道，趕時間咪用有料優先上高速囉，因為自動車道你可以超速，好多時你會快過標個時間好多到達。<br />\nday2蒸餾所5點收工，guide tour最後一場係3點半，你研究下你去唔去得切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁巴打我唔應該買HEP住？"},{"pid":"5fec72ad0da3991efe03b1d2815c15b01875039a","tid":371182,"uid":90152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:34:24.000Z","msg":"其實小樽如果住札幌可以即日來回<br />\n如果唔係有特別酒店<br />\n不如住多晚札幌搬少次酒店"},{"pid":"491012c9347ee6d614e9db960d5d712a9588c2c2","tid":371182,"uid":74012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T13:46:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/p1w89m6c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fp1w89m6c&h=c17cb619&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n架車行左幾多里？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n錶頭九千幾<br />\n唔知洗過未"},{"pid":"4bf48a8cd30a11cb5a40b8c9b42795b71f60959d","tid":371182,"uid":48328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T16:05:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/p1w89m6c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fp1w89m6c&h=c17cb619&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n架車行左幾多里？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n錶頭九千幾<br />\n唔知洗過未</blockquote><br />\n玩得開心d巴打"},{"pid":"79c42ed11a6b7b42546c10d77461166752c4bf6a","tid":371182,"uid":74012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T18:07:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/p1w89m6c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fp1w89m6c&h=c17cb619&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n架車行左幾多里？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n錶頭九千幾<br />\n唔知洗過未</blockquote><br />\n玩得開心d巴打</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同行有個日本朋友係度, 解決左唔少溝通上既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過昨日玩到下午三點鐘就話唔舒服, 跟手送左仿返左札幌。一陣睇怕我要孤身前往富良野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c43f5ab47a4990c8c03c941f742ee541fd7ae8f6","tid":371182,"uid":74012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T09:46:19.000Z","msg":"已還車<br />\n行左400公里入左200蚊油<br />\n但冇開冷氣"},{"pid":"0b1355f69af3d0fae3f20e00426670b5614e2fdb","tid":371182,"uid":74012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T09:48:21.000Z","msg":"今日去美瑛冇行收費公路<br />\n兩日油錢加埋只係貴過單程路費100yen<br />\n<br />\n不過兜到仆街, 渣左成4個鐘一程"},{"pid":"c36af8fa36e110675cd0d9ab998243a48fc02d6c","tid":371182,"uid":48328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T14:43:02.000Z","msg":"愈做功課愈覺得5日太短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8e88512c50998fe1b8ebc050a255414dcdb942d","tid":371182,"uid":8401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T15:20:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>愈做功課愈覺得5日太短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都覺得係。<br />\n<br />\n我第一日1450落機，第五日1500機走。其實前得三日玩。<br />\n<br />\n依家諗住自駕<br />\n第一日新千歲-札幌<br />\n第二日札幌-旭川-美瑛-富良野<br />\n第三日富良野-星野度假村<br />\n第四日星野-札幌-小樽-札幌<br />\n第五日札幌9hea-新千歲<br />\n<br />\n依家諗緊第二日會唔會chur得濟"},{"pid":"de7169c0d40c696f0a889fc7ea84808b581f21e7","tid":371182,"uid":48328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T15:43:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>愈做功課愈覺得5日太短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都覺得係。<br />\n<br />\n我第一日1450落機，